Types of OS:

Batched OS (Example: Payroll System, Transactions Process, etc.
Multi-Programmed OS (Example: Windows O/S, UNIX O/S, etc.)
Timesharing OS (Example: Multics, etc.
Distributed OS (LOCUS, etc.)
Real-Time OS (PSOS, VRTX, etc.)
